{"tid":675821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[咖喱味] 洛馬：印度若製F-16 將成戰機出口樞紐","createTime":"2018-05-24T00:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T04:08:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85c4e21430efbe1c4792ad3941a75ec23450241d","tid":675821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"洛馬：印度若製F-16 將成戰機出口樞紐<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3159091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5641%2F3159091&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbosPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=97800df5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/3159091</a><br />\n<br />\n為爭取印度空軍戰機訂單，美國洛克希德馬丁公司高層今天指出，為印度量身訂製的F-16戰機若能在本地製造，印度將成為戰機出口的樞紐，並附帶1650億美元的維修市場。<br />\n<br />\n洛克希德馬丁（Lockheed Martin）戰略與商業發展副總裁拉爾（Vivek Lall）在「印度新聞信託社」（PTI）表示，洛馬向印度提出F-16的Block 70，將是史上技術最先進、功能最強大的F-16，且採用匿蹤戰機F-35的部分技術。"},{"pid":"446a79c4a15c5830829902b3e34fc7d50f60454f","tid":675821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e54cde17e0381321dbb1e97c51d5c017759ddf4","tid":675821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28d692b06ec9147e7038b3e9e2c6d69d5feb440","tid":675821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b215622b551fd4fa9b72c846f0cc0cd9aa76bc39","tid":675821,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"印度啲軍備八國聯軍咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk